# Visual Studio/dotnet GitIgnore

## Ignore Visual Studio files
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Ignore build outputs
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Log]/

## Ignore Rider/Resharper/JetBrains files
.idea/
*.useroptions

## Ignore packages
packages/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets

## Ignore OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
